description: This file defines a mock class for the SecureStorageService gRPC service, used for testing. It includes mock method declarations for each RPC method in the service.

classes.name: SecureStorageServiceMock
classes.description: A mock class for the SecureStorageService gRPC server, inheriting from the generated service class, with mock methods for testing.

methods.name: ~SecureStorageServiceMock
methods.description: Default destructor for the mock class.

methods.name: GetValue
methods.description: Mock method for the GetValue RPC, retrieves a value from secure storage.

methods.name: UpdateValue
methods.description: Mock method for the UpdateValue RPC, updates a value in secure storage.

methods.name: DeleteValue
methods.description: Mock method for the DeleteValue RPC, deletes a value from secure storage.

methods.name: DeleteAllValues
methods.description: Mock method for the DeleteAllValues RPC, clears all stored values.

methods.name: SeedValue
methods.description: Mock method for the SeedValue RPC, seeds the storage with initial data.
